        <item>
            <title>Elon Musk 正创造世界最强 AI     使用 10 万个 Nvidia GPU 训练 Gork-3</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:30:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gork-3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[xAI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1252286</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Elon Musk 旗下的人工智能公司 xAI 计划在年尾之前推出声称各项性能都是世上最强的人工智能，将使用 10 万个液冷 H100 GPU 组成孟菲斯超级丛集（Memphis Supercluster），并用来训练预计会在年尾推出的 Gork-3。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Glad to be making history with <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@elonmusk</a>, such a great experience to work with his Memphis team! To meet the target, our execution had to be as perfect as possible, as quick as possible, as efficient as possible and as environmentally friendly as possible – lots of hard work, but…</p><p>&mdash; Charles Liang (@charlesliang) <a href="https://twitter.com/charlesliang/status/1815410868433428504?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">July 22, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">xAI 的第一款大模型 Gork-1 于 2023 年 11 月登场，Elon Musk 本月曾宣布会在 8 月推出 Gork-2，如今再透露会使用 10 万个 Nvidia H100 GPU 来训练年尾推出的 Gork-3。这次项目与 Supermicro 合作，后者为 xAI 提供了大部份的硬件，而 Supermicro CEO Charles Liang 亦在 Elon Musk 的推文下留言高度赞场 xAI 团队的执行能力。</p><p>由 10 万个液冷 H100 GPU 组成的孟菲斯超级丛集，相信 GPU 性能上将能轻松超越最新 500 强上的任何东西。至于世界上最强大的超级电脑如 Frontier（37888 个 AMD GPU）、Aurora（60000 个 Intel GPU）和 Microsoft Eagle（14400 个 Nvidia H100 GPU）似乎都会被 xAI 大大抛离。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.tomshardware.com/pc-components/gpus/elon-musk-fires-up-the-most-powerful-ai-training-cluster-in-the-world-uses-100000-nvidia-h100-gpus-on-a-single-fabric">Tom’s Hardware</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://electrek.co/2024/06/04/elon-musk-asked-nvidia-prioritize-gpu-shipments-x-over-tesla-emails/">Electrek</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/tesla-to-have-humanoid-robots-for-internal-use-next-year/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 人形机械人   Elon Musk 确认明年试产供内部使用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/elon-musks-grok-chatbot-keeps-hallucinating-wrong-news/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">藉特朗普遭枪击「创作」假新闻   Elon Musk 旗下 xAI 大型语言模型被狠批</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/elon-musk-21/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 爆料数月内曾被暗杀 2 次    「全力支持特朗普希望他早日康复」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world/ai/">Elon Musk 正创造世界最强 AI     使用 10 万个 Nvidia GPU 训练 Gork-3</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
